titles.title: Dismissing the election contest relating to the office of Representative from the Forty Third Congressional District of California.

action.text: The House Committee on House Administration reported an original measure, H. Rept. 113-133, by Mrs. Miller (MI).

calendar.text: Placed on the House Calendar, Calendar No. 37.

vote.text: On agreeing to the resolution Agreed to without objection.

action.text: Motion to reconsider laid on the table Agreed to without objection.

bill.summary: 6/26/2013--Passed House without amendment. Dismisses the election contest relating to the office of Representative from the Forty-Third Congressional District of California (election contest filed by Project Hurt against incumbent Maxine Waters).
